<item><title>0.106.0</title><link>https://github.com/openai/codex/releases/tag/rust-v0.106.0</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://github.com/openai/codex/releases/tag/rust-v0.106.0</guid><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 23:11:50 GMT</pubDate><description><![CDATA[<p>## New Features
- Added a direct install script for macOS and Linux and publish it as a GitHub release asset, using the existing platform payload (including `codex` and `rg`) (#12740)
